  <h1 style="text-align: center;">Node REST API Landing page</h1>

  <h2>Project Overview</h2>
  <p>This project showcases REST API capabilities for a test model called 'Book'. All functionality is located at REST
    API endpoints. A description of these endpoints and their expected inputs
    can be found below.</p>
  <hr>

  <h2>API Documentation</h2>

  <h3 style="text-decoration: underline;">Find All</h3>
  <p><b>Description: </b>The endpoint lists all records of the 'Books' collection. The response is represented as a list
    of JSON objects.
  </p>
  <p><b>Example URL: </b>http://localhost:3000/api/books/findAll</p>

